buri.ddmsence.ddms.security.ism

Class SecurityAttributes.Builder

  • Object
    • buri.ddmsence.ddms.security.ism.SecurityAttributes.Builder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    SecurityAttributes

    public static class SecurityAttributes.Builder
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Builder for these attributes.

    This class does not implement the IBuilder interface, because the behavior of commit() is at odds with the standard commit() method. As an attribute group, an empty attribute group will always be returned instead of null.

    Since:
    1.8.0
    Author:
    Brian Uri!
    See Also:
    IBuilder, Serialized Form
